$lang['Hexadecimal is a way of representing binary data in human-readable form. It was developed in the 19th century to allow computers to store large amounts of information.'] = 'Hexadecimal ni njia ya kuwakilisha data binary katika umbo linaloweza kusomeka na binadamu. Ilianzishwa katika karne ya 19 ili kuruhusu kompyuta kuhifadhi kiasi kikubwa cha habari.';
$lang['You can use hexadecimal to convert between decimal and binary values. For example, converting 10011011001010 into hexadecimal would result in 0x4F. This means that the value 4F represents the binary number 100110110010110.'] = 'Unaweza kutumia hexadecimal kubadilisha kati ya maadili ya decimal na ya binary. Kwa mfano, kugeuza 10011011001010 kuwa heksadesimali kunaweza kusababisha 0x4F. Hii inamaanisha kuwa thamani 4F inawakilisha nambari ya binary 100110110010110.';
$lang['In mathematics and computer science, hexadecimal (also base 16, or hex) is a positional numeral system with a radix, or base, of 16. It uses sixteen distinct symbols, most often the symbols 0–9 to represent values zero to nine, and A, B, C, D, E, F (or alternatively a–f) to represent values ten to fifteen. For example, the hexadecimal number 2AF3 is equal, in decimal, to (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) , or 10,995.'] = 'Katika hisabati na sayansi ya kompyuta, heksadesimali (pia besi 16, au heksi) ni mfumo wa nambari wa nafasi wenye radix, au besi, ya 16. Hutumia alama kumi na sita tofauti, mara nyingi alama 0-9 kuwakilisha maadili sifuri hadi tisa, na A, B, C, D, E, F (au vinginevyo a–f) kuwakilisha thamani kumi hadi kumi na tano. Kwa mfano, nambari ya hexadecimal 2AF3 ni sawa, kwa decimal, hadi (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) au 10,995.';
$lang['Each hexadecimal digit represents four binary digits (bits) (also called a "nibble"), and the primary use of hexadecimal notation is as a human-friendly representation of binary coded values in computing and digital electronics. For example, byte values can range from 0 to 255 (decimal) but may be more conveniently represented as two hexadecimal digits in the range 00 through FF. Hexadecimal is also commonly used to represent computer memory addresses.'] = 'Kila tarakimu ya heksadesimali inawakilisha tarakimu nne za binary (biti) (pia huitwa &quot;nibble&quot;), na matumizi ya msingi ya nukuu ya heksadesimali ni kama uwakilishi wa kibinadamu wa thamani zilizo na msimbo wa binary katika kompyuta na umeme wa kidijitali. Kwa mfano, thamani za baiti zinaweza kuanzia 0 hadi 255 (desimali) lakini zinaweza kuwakilishwa kwa urahisi zaidi kama tarakimu mbili za heksadesimali katika masafa 00 hadi FF. Hexadecimal pia hutumiwa kwa kawaida kuwakilisha anwani za kumbukumbu za kompyuta.';
$lang['Hex is an abbreviation of Hexadecimal, which is based on a base -16 structure and is used for simplifying how instructions to computers are represented. This 16 symbols number system was developed as a means of inhibiting an 8-bit binary number, so data can be encoded into computers effortlessly. It can be imprinted and typed using two different hex digits with each hex digit demonstrating a nibble or perhaps a 4-bits format.'] = 'Hex ni ufupisho wa Hexadecimal, ambayo inategemea muundo wa msingi -16 na hutumiwa kurahisisha jinsi maagizo kwa kompyuta yanawakilishwa. Mfumo huu wa nambari wa alama 16 ulitengenezwa kama njia ya kuzuia nambari 8-bit, kwa hivyo data inaweza kusimba kwenye kompyuta kwa urahisi. Inaweza kuchapishwa na kuchapwa kwa kutumia tarakimu mbili tofauti za heksi na kila tarakimu ya heksi inayoonyesha nibble au labda umbizo la biti 4.';
$lang['This number system uses 16 symbols that are represented in a range from 0-9 or A-F. The 0–9 represent numbers up to nine whereas A-F is represented by the numeric 10–15. As compared to the other three types of number systems, the hexadecimal numeral system is considered to be the most effective one.'] = 'Mfumo huu wa nambari hutumia alama 16 ambazo zinawakilishwa katika masafa kutoka 0-9 au AF. 0–9 inawakilisha nambari hadi tisa ilhali AF inawakilishwa na nambari 10–15. Ikilinganishwa na aina zingine tatu za mifumo ya nambari, mfumo wa nambari za heksadesimali unachukuliwa kuwa bora zaidi.';
$lang['Your hexadecimal code is invalid'] = 'Msimbo wako wa heksadesimali ni batili';
